<p>Re-test <em>everything</em>:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">./bin/phpunit -c app</div></code></pre>
<p>Now we're green and we can send back exciting error responses from anywhere in our
code. But what about other exceptions, like 404 exceptions?</p>

    
